Package: likert2dummy
Title: Convert 5-pt Likert scale variable to dummy variable
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Anna",
           family = "Santo",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "anna.santo@ubc.ca",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2056-0892"))
Description: The goal of likert2dummy is to turn 5-pt Likert-scale or Likert-type scale items into dummy variables. This function converts 5-pt scales using the rule that a 4 or 5 on a Likert scale will = 1 on the dummy scale, and a 3, 2, or 1 on Likert scale will = 0 on a dummy scale.
